GCKKC1A.original: ~z~I mean, I was born into privilege. I was given an education.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~我是说，我是富人家的孩子，有机会接受教育。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Do you not think that it is vain to think you can make a difference? To think it is your concern?
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~难道你不觉得，认为自己可以发挥作用，认为这是你的责任，是没有意义的吗？

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~I thought it would be like I imagined. But I'm really lonely. I mean, it's nice to be out with you.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~我以为能过上想象中的生活，但实际上我很孤独。我是说，很高兴能和你出来玩。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~The world has rights, just like criminals and murderers and immigrants and all the other disadvantageous do, too.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~地球也有权利，就像罪犯、杀人犯、移民和各种弱势群体一样。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~I mean, it's just the arresting officer's word against the perps. "We found this gun on him."
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~我是说，光靠办案刑警的证词就定罪了。「嫌犯身上有枪。」

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Yes - I knew you'd be nice, from your email.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~没错，我就知道你人很好，看邮件就知道了。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~I was being sarcastic... don't worry about it... who is Dorian?
~z~You're seeing a different side of me meeting me this way. It's working out.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~跟我约会能让你见到我的另一面。挺不错的。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~I'm a girl who wants to make it in the big city. You know, I grew up in the suburbs, bored out of my mind...
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~我是个想在大城市有所成就的女孩。你看，我在郊区长大，从小就很无聊...

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Because some people are having a miserable time, I guess. I don't know.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~可能是因为还有人在经历不幸吧。我也不知道。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~What do you mean? Who have you been talking to?
~z~"His clothes were covered in the victim's blood." An innocent man with a felony prior doesn't stand a chance.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~「他的衣服沾满了受害者的血。」曾犯重罪的良民是没有机会的。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~I came here and I thought it would be different.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~我来这里时以为这里会不一样。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Don't you sometimes feel really guilty driving a car?
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~你开车的时候会不会感到很内疚？

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~It doesn't matter why you do something as long as it's right.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~只要你的行为正确，动机就不重要。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~I'm a go getter, Niko. A real Alpha female.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~我是个上进的人，Niko。真正的一流女人。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~The only guys I meet are the other lawyers - complete creeps - and my defendants.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~能见到的只有我讨厌的其他律师，和我的委托人。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~There will always be people who suffer, Kiki. That is the way of the world.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~总会有人遭遇不幸的，Kiki。这个世界就是如此。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~I'm going to warn you Niko, I'm not in the best of moods.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~先跟你说好，Niko，我现在心情很差。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~this is so unlike me, but I'm giving it a go and it seems to be working out.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~这太不像我会做的事了，但我试了一试，似乎也还不错。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~All your ex-boyfriends seem to be real pacifists...
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~你的前男友好像都是真正的和平主义者...

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Sometimes, when I'm having a fun time - even a fun time with a crazy man like you, I feel so guilty.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~有时候，即便我很开心，我还是会感到内疚，哪怕是跟你这样的好人在一起的时候。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~You can try. Most of the people from my law class just went to big firms on the Exchange to make their millions.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~不试试怎么知道。跟我同专业的同学大多去了证交区的大公司，年入百万。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Because of the carbon footprint, because of future generations, of course.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~因为产生了碳足迹，还会祸害子孙后代。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Like I said, this is so unlike me.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~我也说了，这太不像我会做的事了。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~None that are still on the outside. This government really annoys me, Niko.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~他们全都进去了。政府真的很让我恼火，Niko。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Relationships can't rarely last when they get sent out of state to a Federal Penitentiary though.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~不过等他们被送进联邦监狱以后，这段感情就难以维系了。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~What made you decide to look for love online?
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~你为什么会选择在网上寻找爱情？

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~It's nearly impossible for a man born into poverty in this country to make it without breaking the law.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~在这个国家，穷人家的孩子不犯法是很难成功的。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~But he's a survivor. I'm trying to get him to write a book about it.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~但他挺住了。我建议他把自己的经历写成书。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~I wanted to help people. That's why I do pro bono work at City Hall.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~我想帮助别人，所以才会去市政厅做无偿法律援助。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Yeah, really sweet guys - misunderstood, you know?
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~是啊，都是些好人，只是不被理解，懂吧？

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~He's got such soul. Being unfairly incarcerated would break most men.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~他有高洁的灵魂。大多数人含冤入狱后都会崩溃，

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~I'm starting to understand why you're seeing me, I think.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~我大概有点明白你为什么肯见我了。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~He's serving life upstate. Can you believe that they revoked his conjugal visit privileges? It's inhuman.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~在北方终身监禁。他的配偶探望权居然还被剥夺了。太没人性了。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~If he does write one, I'll read it.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~他能写出来的话，我会拜读的。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Finding the whole internet dating thing? I mean,
~z~Just sometimes I feel like I can't do enough though. I feel like I can't help people as much as I want to be able to.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~不过有时我会觉得自己做得还不够，帮助他人时时常感觉心有余而力不足。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~It's an absolute farce the miscarriages of justice that he's had to suffer.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~让他承受正义缺失的代价实在荒谬。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~I'm a criminal, and a murderer. I arrived in your country and fell in with a bad crowd. What rights do I have?
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~我是一个罪犯，还是杀人犯。我来到你们国家，和不法分子厮混。我能有什么权利？

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~I don't know, I just thought I'd try it. What made you?
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~我不知道，我只是想试试。那你呢？

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~It sounds as if you're being as helpful as you can be.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~听起来你好像在尽可能地帮助别人。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~I try not to lose touch though.
~z~I don't pretend that I wouldn't be selling my ass for crack if I was born in project housing though.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~要是我出生在公屋社区，多半也会为了毒品出卖肉体。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~It was a conspiracy. The government doesn't like free thinkers and autodidacts.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~这是个阴谋。政府不喜欢思想自由的人和无师自通的人。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~I defend the people that the rest of the community has forgotten about.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~我会为那些被社会遗忘的人辩护。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~As I see it, I have chosen to live life outside the law. Rights mean nothing to me now.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~在我看来，既然选择了当法外之徒，权利就对我毫无意义了。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Not everyone born in a project sells their ass for crack.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~出生在公屋社区的人未必会为了毒品卖身。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Well, sometimes the cops are bigger crooks than the guys they're arresting.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~嗯，有些警察确实比被捕的犯人还坏。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~I cannot take grown men playing dressing up games very seriously.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~我不喜欢看一群成年人在那里过家家。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~This ex of mine, Mitch, I met him when I represented him on this bogus murder charge.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~我前男友，Mitch，替他处理谋杀冤案时认识的。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Yeah, I guess I do make a difference. I feel like all my life I've been given things by my parents.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~是啊，我大概确实有所改变。感觉我这辈子一直在接受父母的给予。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Oh... ummm... nothing. Have you got any ex-boyfriends I should worry about?
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~噢...呃...没什么。我需要担心你的哪个前男友吗？

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Mom and Dad made me promise not to date any more of them so here I am, dating on the internet.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~爸妈让我保证不再跟这些人约会，所以我现在搞网恋。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~I'm so sorry! Our society let you down! My country failed you!
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~真对不起！我们的社会让你失望了！我的国家辜负了你！

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~I mean, Mitch was no angel. I'm not going to pretend that he was.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~的确，Mitch不算是好人，这点我不否认。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~If I got hauled down to City Hall, I'd be grateful for your help.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~如果我被扭送市政厅，我就会感谢你的帮助。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~But, well... it was nice. It's strange. You always want something to be like it is in the movies, don't you?
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~但是，嗯...普通就好。很奇怪，你会不会期待生活偶尔像电影情节一样发展？

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~So, Niko, are there any skeletons in your closet? Is anyone haunting you?
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~那，Niko，你有什么不可告人的秘密吗？有人缠着你吗？

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~How can I be grateful when I'm in so much pain?
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~我这么痛苦，怎么高兴的起来？

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~But it was obviously self defense. A mother clearly attacked him, and he shot her, and her kids.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~但明明是正当防卫。那个母亲攻击了他，他掏枪反击，还打中了两个孩子。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~I'm an idealist, if that's what you mean.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~我想你的意思是我是个理想主义者吧。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~I represent the people who can't even help themselves.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~我代表那些甚至都无法自救的人。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~You're a noble savage. You should sue the government.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~你是个高尚的莽夫。你应该起诉政府。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~The line is so blurry. I'm too close to be able to tell what he is.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~界线太模糊了。当局者迷，我区分不了。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~It's not bad luck Niko. It's the system. It's totally fucked. Totally.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~这不是倒霉，Niko，是体制问题。体制烂了，完全烂了。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~He's such a big softie. He's practically Buddhist.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~他心肠很好的，几乎是一个佛教徒。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Thank you, Niko, I knew you'd understand.
~z~And now I'm here, trying to make a difference. I'm not naïve... but...
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~现在我进城了，想要有所改变。不是我太幼稚...但...

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Cars, clothes, my apartment, my education. I help the people who haven't been given anything.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~车子，衣服，我的公寓，我的教育。现在我帮助那些无法得到给予的人。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~I mean, are there any ex-girlfriends who are still hung up on you? What did you think I meant?
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~我是说，有没有哪个前女友现在还对你死缠烂打？你以为我是什么意思？

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~It might be because I feel guilty but is that a bad thing? Am I doing it for the wrong reasons?
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~可能是出于内疚，但这有关系吗？难道我的动机就错了吗？

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~But I feel so guilty. Life is so unfair.
~z~I could just tell... I mean, not that I read too much into it. This is just a casual date, you know. Casual.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~就是能看出来嘛...也不是说我过度解读了。反正这次就是个普通约会而已。普通约会。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Client / ex, ex / client, lover, friend, spiritual guru.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~委托人兼前任，前任兼委托人，爱人，朋友，精神导师。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Unlucky though. Hopefully that won't rub off on me.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~真是倒霉。好在我应该不会被传染。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Yeah, only Tremaine was completely innocent. There's no way he killed those guys.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~是啊，但Tremaine是完全无辜的。他不可能杀那些人。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~Triple homicide - well that was what he was accused of.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~谋杀三人——这就是他的被控罪名。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~It's just that I'm working these cases the whole time and I can't get out to meet new people.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~只是因为我每天忙着打官司，没空出去交新朋友。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~You two have so much in common, I mean more than just me. You're both such peace loving men.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~你们两个有很多共同点，不只是都和我处得好。你们都是爱好和平的人。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~The world is certainly determined to screw itself up.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~这个世界注定是会走向毁灭的。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~But the police will arrest any man in the vicinity of a crime in order to clear a file from their desks.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~但那些警察为了尽快结案，只会在案发现场附近随便抓一个人。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~It was stupid. It just goes to show how the system is primed to punish people who already disadvantaged.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~说来可笑，他的经历只会证明，现有体制旨在惩罚弱势群体。

GCKKC1A.original: ~z~And you've come out okay - you should be grateful.
GCKKC1A.translated: ~z~但你的命不差啊，你应该高兴才对。
